  <h1>Welcome to RecipeShare!</h1>

  <p>RecipeShare is an online recipe book for you to share and store your favorite recipes.</p>
  <p>It's so easy to lose track of those favorite recipes when they're lost in a
    multitude of books or tossed into a box. With RecipeShare you can post all
    of your favorite recipes, add photos, link to the source, and add tags for
    organization. Not only will you have all of your favorite recipes in one place, but
    you'll be able to browse and save the favorite recipes of others, too! </p>
