    <h4><strong>So, how does it work?</strong></h4>
    <p>Easy! Create an account with your email, or just log in through Facebook.
      On our <%= link_to 'Recipes', recipes_path %> page you'll be able to browse already
      created recipes and add your own.</p>
      <p><strong>To add your own recipe:</strong></p>
      <ul class="ul-center">
        <li>Add your recipe title. (This can be anything!)</li>
        <li>Add the recipe ingredients, preferably with bullet points. (This keeps it nice and tidy!)</li>
        <li>Add the instructions in a numbered list. (So no one loses track of what step they should be on!)</li>
        <li>Add the source. (Favorite chef, blog, cooking site, your own kitchen? Add it and give them (or you) credit!)</li>
        <li>Upload a photo. (We want to know what the final product should look like!)</li>
        <li>Add descriptive tags for the recipe. (Meat? Fish? Dessert? Chocolate? Make it easy to sort through all the amazing recipe options!)</li>
